title: Sibling Advicery: Homecoming Dates/Boring Boardgames
description:
This week Bob and Monét are back with some advice to listeners. Tune in to hear the about all the Patreon drama, potential plans to open a Brick and Mortar, and advice on dealing with a partner with boring hobbies, imposter syndrome, and on the fence homecoming dates.
